""" Key maps

" Move between windows
nnoremap <c-j> <c-w>j
nnoremap <c-k> <c-w>k
nnoremap <c-h> <c-w>h
nnoremap <c-l> <c-w>l
" Esc
inoremap jj <Esc>
vnoremap jj <Esc>

""" Colours

" Syntax
syntax enable

""" Spacing

" Visual spaces per tab
set tabstop=4
" Spaces per tab when editing
set softtabstop=4
